OL,3,CThree convicted after mother-of-eight
OL,4,Cflung from funfair ride and left in
OL,5,Ccoma
OL,7,FThe Health and Safety Executive
OL,8,Fpublished the footage after its
OL,9,Fprosecution of a firm and three
OL,10,Findividuals.
OL,12,FThe owners and manufacturers of a have
OL,13,Fbeen handed suspended sentences after
OL,14,Fa woman was seriously injured when she
OL,15,Fcatapulted from one of their rides.
OL,17,FFootage has now been released by the
OL,18,FHealth and Safety Executive of Khadra
OL,19,FAli as she was flung from the
OL,20,FXcelerator ride at the Funderpark
OL,21,Ffunfair in Yiewsley in 2018.
