OL,3,CThree convicted after mother-of-eight
OL,4,Cflung from funfair ride and left in
OL,5,Ccoma
OL,7,FThe mother-of-eight was left in a coma
OL,8,Fand spent four months in hospital. She
OL,9,Fsuffered multiple fractures to her
OL,10,Fback, hips, pelvis, ribs and both
OL,11,Fcollarbones, as well as internal
OL,12,Fbleeding and a significant head injury.
OL,14,FThe owner of the ride, Derek Hackett,
OL,15,Fmanufacturer Perrin Stevens, and David
OL,16,FGeary, whose company was responsible
OL,17,Ffor safety checks, all pleaded guilty
OL,18,Ftoover the incident.
