OL,3,CThree convicted after mother-of-eight
OL,4,Cflung from funfair ride and left in
OL,5,Ccoma
OL,7,FAll three received suspended prison
OL,8,Fsentences and were ordered to pay tens
OL,9,Fof thousands in costs.
OL,11,FMrs Ali, who was 45 at the time, went
OL,12,Fon the ride with her daughter but was
OL,13,Fnot suitably restrained in her seat.
OL,15,FAs the ride picked up speed, she
OL,16,Fscreamed for help and clung on for
OL,17,Fsome time before being ejected. She
OL,18,Fhit the barrier of the next ride and
OL,19,Flanded on the ground.
