OL,7,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,8,Ffound the rider's seat restraint
OL,9,Fsystem was designed with electrical
OL,10,Fand mechanical failings. The ride
OL,11,Fcontrol system was set up in such a
OL,12,Fway that it would not have detected
OL,13,Fthe failure.
OL,15,FThe was also found not to be properly
OL,16,Fmaintained or monitored.
