OL,4,Cflung from funfair ride and left in
OL,5,Ccoma
OL,7,FCrucially, the operator did not check
OL,8,Feach rider's restraint bar before
OL,9,Fstarting the ride, as they should
OL,10,Fhave. They also did not notice that
OL,11,FMrs Ali required assistance, at which
OL,12,Fpoint the ride should have been
OL,13,Fstopped.
OL,15,FA statement from Mrs Ali's
OL,16,Frepresentative said the family was
OL,17,F"deeply relieved that the criminal
OL,18,Fprosecution has concluded following
OL,19,Fthe tragic incident at the Funderpark
OL,20,FFun Fair."
